Nemesis Enforcer:




Nemesis Enforcer took out his rapid-firing laser rifle from subspace, the 
weapon appearing in his left hand, an energon blade appearing in his right 
hand.

Making sure to yell over the autogun fire, Nemesis Enforcer looked to 
Soundwave. 

"The Matrix has spoke to me, you blasphemer, it wants you dead, and Cybertron 
to continue to be non-organic!  It's will will be acted upon!  See you in the 
Pit!" Nemesis gave a lopsided grin, firing off ten rapid laser bolts at 
Soundwave's pelvis.
